OOC: Okay

BIC:
Speedbreaker reaches the height of his jump, as gravity starts to pull
him down. Beastbox coils, crouching inwards like a snake ready to
strike. And he does. He extedns his legs, leaping quickly, and strongly.
He leaves Speedbreaker, and continues towards Incinerator like a
balistic missile, and fires twice out of his shoulder cannons at him, as
he nears.


Speedbreaker begins to fall towards the ground, and transforms. He then
flies down towards Shockwave.
